title: President Dr. Joyce Hedlund on Medical Leave (University of Maine at Machias)
text: ( Source : University of Maine at Machias ) Added on: October 21 , 2015 MACHIAS, Maine -- Dr. Joyce Hedlund, 67, Interim President of the University of Maine at Machias, was admitted to Eastern Maine Medical Center in Bangor this past weekend
